    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>**《太空猫纸牌》** 是一场充满谜题与冒险精神的卡牌游戏，背景设定在一个欢乐的、充满80年代复古未来风的宇宙世界——当然，少不了猫咪的陪伴。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175050/extras/c175d198b46aeae850d30e6aebad1332.poster.avif?t=1772347788\" width=616 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175050/extras/c175d198b46aeae850d30e6aebad1332.webm?t=1772347788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175050/extras/c175d198b46aeae850d30e6aebad1332.mp4?t=1772347788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >忘掉你奶奶教你的那套老派接龙吧——这些太空猫可要带你体验一场全新的宇宙级冒险！发挥你的智慧与策略，完成任务、赚取喵索、解锁超赞奖励。各种独特的玩法与类Roguelike元素让每一局都焕然一新。顶级猫科飞行员学员还将获得与当地集群古怪居民一起进行的激动人心的故事任务和冒险——包括各种恶作剧。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> 技术为王，不靠运气！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大多数牌局都能赢，只要你够聪明！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想轻松散步还是挑战高难？全由你决定！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持无限撤销，让你放心尝试各种策略，随时反败为喵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175050/extras/e93e5299b77ea89b8d904772f41e7c05.poster.avif?t=1772347788\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175050/extras/e93e5299b77ea89b8d904772f41e7c05.webm?t=1772347788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175050/extras/e93e5299b77ea89b8d904772f41e7c05.mp4?t=1772347788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>赢取喵喵大奖！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成特别挑战赢取奖杯，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >或用辛苦赚来的奖励为你的专属太空小猫装点个性！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >闪闪发亮的奖品、毛茸茸的快乐！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175050/extras/974c2e63e3b5a4b770c8384a3f256207.poster.avif?t=1772347788\" width=616 height=476 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175050/extras/974c2e63e3b5a4b770c8384a3f256207.webm?t=1772347788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175050/extras/974c2e63e3b5a4b770c8384a3f256207.mp4?t=1772347788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>享受旅程的每一刻</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论是悠然整理牌堆的节奏感、连招爆发的爽快感，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还是胜利时的庆典喵叫，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一刻都像是在温暖阳光下舒展毛爪。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175050/extras/dcaa7182f9da0702093d57f5d31c41f0.poster.avif?t=1772347788\" width=616 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175050/extras/dcaa7182f9da0702093d57f5d31c41f0.webm?t=1772347788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3175050/extras/dcaa7182f9da0702093d57f5d31c41f0.mp4?t=1772347788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> 内容超新星爆发！</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特又清新的新机制（这可不是你奶奶的接龙）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种难度，适合各类玩家</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冒险模式：真正的Roguelike体验！携带强化道具挑战递增难度，风险与奖励并存！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家统计 &amp; 图表，记录你的胜利喵迹——还能和朋友（以及他们的猫）分享！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可解锁的奖杯与装饰，打造你的专属太空猫！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >剧情任务：章节式冒险，追随太空猫的首次星际之旅！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >太空、猫，还有接龙。完美组合</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于开发者</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在为他人从事了多年令人心碎的数据科学工作后，Gray Duck Games 诞生了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >怀揣着儿时的梦想，手里拿着遣散费，Gray Duck (Clive) 自学了编程、Unity、矢量图形、音效设计和图像编辑——所有这些都是为了制作他的第一款游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《太空猫纸牌》并非“梦想游戏”；它是一款用心创作的作品，融合了他最热爱的两大事物：猫咪、太空和解谜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clive 活跃于 Gray Duck Games 的 Discord 社区。分享你的猫咪照片，加入我们，共同期待游戏的发布！ :)</p>",
